title: I’m making recovery dnp gcs!
body:
Hey! I don’t know if my blog is active enough for things like this but I’m making or at least just attempting to make gcs!

So what’s it all about?

We all miss dan and phil (well, mostly dan) and the hiatus for sure makes us sad. So let’s come together and spread positive vibes! In this gcs we will discuss, of course, dnp and other topics that make us feel better. Why gcS? I will make several of them so everyone can be comfortable with their new pals (it will depend on age and shipping). And don’t worry you don’t have to tell everyone about your problems etc., you can just be there for someone else!

Who can join the gc?

Everyone who feels like they want to discuss dnp and make some new friends!

How can I join?

Fill –>this<– form. I’ll read your preferences and find the gc you’ll feel comfortable to be a part of! 

When can I join?

I’ll be accepting forms for 3 weeks - till June 12.

Hope to see you soon! <3

{ credits: toxiclolley88 - x }

summary: So, I was doing an art project, and...though I was referencing off a female example, it started looking more like a male. And...
body:
So, I was doing an art project, and…though I was referencing off a female example, it started looking more like a male. And then suddenly it started looking like Dan?? ( because I’m a lowkey sad and thirsty Dannie who misses the boye so much that he is lit-rally half of my brain ) So I decided to make it Dan, and tell my father I thought of the guy off the top of my head…😂 I didn’t really have one reference picture, I just looked at 2 side angle pics of him once or twice, so it’s not 100% accurate haha…BUT IM SO ASHAMED PROUD OF IT~!! ItS NoT bAd~!! So then I was like: hey since everyone misses Dan like I do let’s post it~! 🖤🖤🖤🥺🥺🥺

( the third time I tried taking a picture of it, it got wet because I’d set it on a wet table outside and now it’s ruined…😢 GOOD THING I GOT A PIC~ )
